            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲主要股市收市下跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數報23534點，跌131點，跌幅近0.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數報7795點，跌32點，跌幅0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數報9213點，跌36點，跌近0.4%。</p>\n</div>",
